  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy of Local Anesthesia in Emergency Inguinal Hernia Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Safety and Efficacy of Local Anesthesia in Emergency Inguinal Hernia Surgery, a Prospective Randomized Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
